Description:
    Creates a scaffold for a Gooey:Group relation

Example:
    rails generate gooey:group_scaffold Page

    This will create:
      Model: app/model/page.rb
      Controller: app/controllers/pages_controller.rb
      Test:       test/controllers/pages_controller_test.rb
      Views:      app/views/pages/index.html.erb [...]
      Helper:     app/helpers/pages_helper.rb
